abstract: Mike Hale reviews Comedy Central series Big Time in Hollywood, FL, starring Kathy Baker and Stephen Tobolowsky.
lead_paragraph: This first serialized, scripted comedy for Comedy Central follows brothers who face a crazy chain of events after being kicked out of their parents’ house.
